reviewText: Came quick, good buisness movie was ok. I love kusugi
Not happy with this DVD it has a flaw,it stops playing about half way through. I have tried it on 3 different players with the same result.
Great movie. Even if you have never seen this movie before buy it. Its great!

I think this was  a great movie 20 years ago, I was just a kid when I saw this and pretty much I love it! Now I am on my 40s and watching this I just said HUH! But still entertaining, same way as Revenge of the Ninja, not so much sophistication but still worth watching!

I remember seeing this movie when I was a kid and wanted to see it again now. I bought the DVD which says its an all region compatible disc. The conversion to DVD though is very bad as everything is so dark and the view looks like it's been copied ten times from a VHS tape. Other than that it's the same movie you may remember.
